# IpcRendererEvent Object extends `Event`

- `sender` [IpcRenderer](/docs/latest/api/ipc-renderer) - The `IpcRenderer` instance that emitted the event originally
- `ports` [MessagePort](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessagePort)\[\] - A list of MessagePorts that were transferred with this message
